#10 Email spoofing

Summary: SPF records are missing, and that leads to email spoofing.
Steps to reproduce: Visit : "https://www.kitterman.com/spf/validate.html/". Then enter the domain name(hack-yourself-first.com) and click "Get SPF Record (if any)" and you will see "No valid SPF record found.". Now you can use any email spoofing tool to spoof emails to the victim.
Impact: Due to this bug, an attacker can send fake emails to the victim and redirect them to phishing pages and steal credentials.
